    <!-- Welcome / First Launch -->
    <string name="welcome_title">Bariev yeq</string>
    <string name="welcome_sovereignty">Dzer banalinern en.\nDzer mijocrn en.\nDzer inkisvanutyunn e.</string>
    <string name="welcome_desc">Dzer mijocrn CHEK pahelum ays cragrum. Narank goyutyun unen blokcheynumy, karvaryum dzer masnavar banalinnerov.\n\nAys cragiry miaynavk pahum e dzer banalinern anvtang. Menk chenk karogh mtunel dzer mijocrn.\n\nCannoti: Vorosh tokenner (USDC, USDT) karogh en saravcel irenk tekaroghnerovn. Amenayn inkisvanutyun hamar ogtagorceck bnakann ETH kam apatkeyntratsvogh tokenner.</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_title">Dzer banalinern = Dzer mijocrn</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_desc">Ete korcrnek dzer masnavar banalinern kam kiseq dranq voreve mekin, duk kocrnek verahskoghutyuny dzer mijocrner vra mshtalapes.\n\nVerakanguman tarbarak chka. Oci ajakcutyun tjimi chenk karogh ognel dzez. Ays e ishakan tirochu bnuytsy.\n\nMisht paheck dzer banalinern anvtang pahustacrum.</string>
    <string name="welcome_opensource">Bats kodn cragrakanum. Stvugeck, mi vsteceq.</string>
    <string name="welcome_start">Haskacom em, sksenq</string>

